  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "What are Route Guards?"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "Route guards are functions that run before or during navigation to control access to routes in a Vue application."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Types of Route Guards"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "value": {
        "headers": ["Type", "Usage"],
        "rows": [
          ["Global Guards", "Applied to all routes"],
          ["Per-Route Guards", "Defined inside route config"],
          ["In-Component Guards", "Defined inside components"]
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Global Before Guard"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "javascript",
      "value": "router.beforeEach((to, from, next) => {\n  if (to.meta.requiresAuth && !isAuthenticated) {\n    next('/login');\n  } else {\n    next();\n  }\n});"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Per-Route Guard"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "javascript",
      "value": "{\n  path: '/admin',\n  component: Admin,\n  beforeEnter: (to, from, next) => {\n    if (!isAdmin) next('/');\n    else next();\n  }\n}"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "In-Component Guard"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "javascript",
      "value": "beforeRouteEnter(to, from, next) {\n  next(vm => {\n    // access component instance\n  });\n}"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Common Use Cases"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "value": [
        "**Authentication check**",
        "**Authorization control**",
        "**Redirecting users**",
        "**Preventing access to certain routes**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Navigation Flow"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "Guards run in sequence before navigation is confirmed, allowing control over routing behavior."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Best Practices"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "value": [
        "**Use global guards for auth checks**",
